description.en: This beautiful dish garden includes a variety of beautiful living plants planted and organized in a way to be visually calming and appealing. Our Premium dish garden is large and abundant with quality plants that are sure to make a lasting impression.

This lush peace lily is the perfect plant to send to celebrate today's special occasion. A favorite among From You Flowers' customers because of its easy care requirements and deep green foliage. Available for delivery to an office or a home. Hand arranged in a bamboo planter this is the perfect gift to celebrate any occasion.

This Auspicious Money Tree is the perfect gift for a friend, neighbor, or loved one. No matter the occasion, this thoughtful plant is sure to bring them the best luck and fortune they can imagine! This tree thrives best indoors with medium to bright indirect light and deep but infrequent watering.

The Japanese Juniper Bonsai Tree arrives planted in a ceramic planter and is a perfect gift for any occasion. These hardy Bonsai plants are forgiving of less than ideal conditions, and have a lovely foliage pattern that lends itself to trimming. This stunning plant will do well outdoors in temperatures above 15 degrees and with protection. Unfortunately, state agricultural regulations prohibit us from shipping these trees to California.

Succulents are super trendy right now, so why not send your most fashion forward friend this ultra modern succulent garden? These hearty, easy to take care of plants make a perfect addition to a desk or as a statement piece in any room!

A timeless gardenia plant is the perfect gift for a budding botanist, celebrating friend, or grieving loved one. This gorgeous live plant features soft white blooms that bloom full and fragrant from May through September. The Gardenia plant has been used in perfumes for centuries, and has continued to be cultivated widely due to its extreme beauty and relative hardiness. Unfortunately, Agricultural Regulations prohibit us from shipping Gardenias to Arizona.

This stunning azalea plant has been carefully crafted into a balanced bonsai shape. The charming tree features beautiful pink blossoms, ready to bloom in the months of May and June! They'll surely cherish this charming, thoughtful gift as it brings light and love into their home. Treat them to a stunning surprise for any occasion with next day delivery options.

A stunning succulent jade plant will bring a sweet smile to your friend, co-worker, or loved one's face. This hardy indoor bonsai tree with a sturdy trunk and lush green leaves grows quickly and beautifully in both low and high light conditions. A lush foliage plant makes a lasting and natural gift, and always brings a smile to their day. This elegant white orchid bring a sense of modernity and class to any room, office, or desk space. Symbolizing beauty, elegance, and faith, this dainty orchid is the perfect choice to add a touch of sophistication. Taking care of this plant is easy, too. Simply keep away from drafts, and water once a week, by just adding ice! Three ice cubes per orchid will do the trick, and it will thrive best in indirect sunlight.

A stunning orchid plant that will brighten any space, and leave a smile on any face. Simply keep away from drafts, and water once a week, by just adding ice! Three ice cubes per orchid will do the trick, and it will thrive best in indirect sunlight.

Send this elegant, pure white orchid to let your recipient know that they are in your thoughts. Whether to send condolences or just to say that you miss them, this plant expresses everything that words can't. Care of this delicate plant is easy! Just place in a bright room out of direct sunlight and away from drafts. Temperatures should remain above 65 degrees Fahrenheit. To water, simply place three ice cubes per orchid in the pot once a week!

This stunning bromeliad is the perfect gift for a friend, co-worker, or loved one! It is prized for its lush green foliage and bright, tropical flowers, as well as being a hardy and easy to care for houseplant. The bold orange blooms will bring light and joy to their office or home. Whether they're celebrating a joyous occasion, or mourning the loss of a loved one, this beautiful plant is the perfect touch.

This product also comes with an expert care guide to help you every step of the way. All in all, this is the best gift for Valentine's Day, Mother's Day, Birthdays, Anniversaries, and more! Plus, this Bromeliad ships fresh from the greenhouse in our expert packaging!

The money tree is aptly named, as it is traditionally seen as an auspicious plant which brings money and fortune to the receiver. This stunning, hardy, plant is full of lush green foliage above twisted branches and will look beautiful in any room of your lucky loved one's home.

This stunning money tree is delivered in a chic gray container that will look stunning in your friend or loved one's home or office. A gorgeous indoor plant, this money tree is said to bring good fortune and prosperity. It is also hardy and easy to care for. Simple give your beauty medium to bright indirect light, and deep but infrequent watering.

Send this simple token of good luck to anyone who needs it! The several trunks are braided together in order to symbolize the "locking in" of good fortune or luck. Care of this plant is easy! Just place in a bright room out of direct sunlight and away from drafts. Temperatures should be between 65-85 degrees Fahrenheit, and should never dip below 55 degrees. To water, simply place two ice cubes in the pot once a week!

Sending best wishes to a friend or loved one for a Happy Birthday or other festive occasion? This Money Tree bonsai is a traditional symbol of good fortune and will wonderfully communicate your feelings in a time-honored way. It is easy and beautiful to grow in all light locations; this bonsai is a good choice for novice plant lovers.

The braided money tree is a classic gifting plant, symbolic of fortune, affluence, and good luck! This charming plant makes a great housewarming, congratulations, or I'm thinking of you gift! It is also wonderfully easy to care for. Simply provide your twisted beauty with plenty of indirect light and ensure you are giving it infrequent but deep watering. It will do best if you wait until the soil is at least half dry, and then water heavily until water is running from the drainage holes.

This chic bouquet pairs super trendy succulents with traditional roses and carnations to create something truly one of a kind for your recipient! They are sure to love this ultra-modern arrangement, no matter the occasion! Approximately 10" H x 10" W.

This plant is commonly known as an Echeveria Succulent. Pot measures 5 inches in diameter. Pot + plant measures ~6.5" in height.
